title: Daigasso! Band Brothers Song Compilation
description:
Daigasso! Band Brothers Song Compilation
===============================================================================

This is a compilation of songs from the 2004 rythm game Daigasso! Band Brothers
for the Nintendo DS. It includes all songs in the "JPOP" and "TV" categories, 
plus all songs from the 2005 expansion pack.

All songs are tagged properly, and their track number corresponds to their 
in-game position. The gap between track 10 and 18 is the "World" category which
is not included as they are mostly custom composed medleys.



Tracklist is as follows:
